modName: Switch Stats between orcish and dwemer
summary: Switches the stats between dwarven and orcish armor and weapons
descriptionHtml: I always found it odd that the orcs that are famous for fighting had worse weapons and the dwarves that are famous for armor had worse armor so i switched them
author: X2Brute
